race.description: Sportsbet Nobody Does It Easier Maiden Plate
race.comment: GAZELLE (12) continues to build nicely, finishing just a nose off the winner at Strathalbyn last time. With Milnes sticking and fitness peaking, she looks hard to beat. FLYING SHELBY (1) was prominent before boxing on into fourth at Hamilton over the mile. The drop back in trip suits, and from the inside draw he maps to get every favour. BANYAN JENNI (7) failed at Warrnambool when resuming but this looks a more suitable assignment. Expect sharp improvement. IMACREEDYTWO (2) was below his best last start but his Mortlake run two back was full of merit when charging late. Will get back from the draw and be saved for one run, capable of finishing over the top if the tempo is genuine.
